title: #49 - Captain Disillusion
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we are joined by the hero of skeptics around the world- Captain Disillusion! We discuss how to sort reality from fiction, deepfakes, and we take a call from an angry Logan Paul fan. Captain Disillusion, aka Alan Melikdjanian, is a very talented YouTube content creator who puts out videos that deconstruct fake videos and memes.
